            "title": "〈台股開盤〉台積電率權值股上攻 一度漲逾350點重返年線",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台股今 (20) 日隨著美股四大指數同步反彈，台積電等權值電子股領軍上攻，開盤即大漲超過 200 點，最高達 22315 點，漲幅達 355 點，一舉站回年線大關。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>權值股今日普遍走強，台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>)(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TSM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TSM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TSM-US</a>) 昨日下探 950 元，今日在低接買盤搶進下，強漲超過 2%，收復年線關卡，市值也回升至<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/usdtwd\">新台幣</a> 25.3 兆元，聯發科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2454:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2454\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2454-TW</a>)、鴻海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2317:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2317\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2317-TW</a>) 漲幅也都在 1% 左右。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>其他如富邦金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2881:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2881\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2881-TW</a>)、國泰金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2882:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2882\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2882-TW</a>)、台達電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2308:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2308\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2308-TW</a>)、廣達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2382:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2382\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2382-TW</a>)、日月光投控 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3711:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3711\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3711-TW</a>)(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ASX:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ASX\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ASX-US</a>) 與聯電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2303:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2303\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2303-TW</a>)(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:UMC:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/UMC\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">UMC-US</a>) 等，漲幅都在 1-2% 左右，推升整體大盤走勢。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>另外，隨著輝達釋出最新 CPO 交換器，並點名多家台廠，當中的波若威 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3163:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3163\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3163-TW</a>) 今日強攻漲停板，創下歷史新高價，達 196.5 元，其他概念股如 IET-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4971:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4971\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4971-TW</a>) 同樣亮燈，訊芯 - KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6451:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6451\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6451-TW</a>)、聯亞 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3081:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3081\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3081-TW</a>) 漲幅都達半根以上，族群漲勢一致。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
